<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Melee configuration</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
[Song1]           [Song2]<br>
[Song3]           [Song4]<br>
[Track]            [Attack]<br>
[Primary hand] [Secondary hand]<br>
[Bag 1]            [open inventory spot]<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Charm Kiting Config</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
[Song1]           [Song2]<br>
[Song3]           [Song4]<br>
[Track]            [/pet attack]<br>
[Primary hand] [Secondary hand]<br>
[Bag 1]            [Open inventory spot]<br>
<br>
I juggle my weapons and instruments back and forth between my hands, the bag, and the open inventory slot.<br>
<br>
When twisting, I just click the buttons once to activate the song, and then twice to change to the next song.  So it goes<br>
<br>
1, 5 sec pause<br>
2,2, 5 sec pause<br>
3,3, 5 sec pause<br>
1,1, 5 sec pause<br>
2,2, 5 sec pause<br>
3,3, 5 sec pause<br>
etc.<br>
<br>
Charm kiting varies somewhat, since I use accelerating chorus which lasts 90 seconds, and the charms last about 30 seconds.  Mostly I'm twisting my 2 regen songs and interspersing charm or selo's as needed.<br>
<br>
